txt.en: Throne of the Dread Terror: Unbound Corruption

The Unbroken One stands alone in defiance of the sorcerers of Minas Morgul. Only when his corruption is fully drained can you defeat those still under the thrall of the Black Numenóreans.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This deed can only be completed on Tier 2 of the Throne of the Dread Terror raid.</rgb>
